    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >部落领袖</h2>滑鼠简单操控部落酋长。分配工作，发展经济，养兵千日，统一美洲大陆。<br><br>与传统的RTS游戏不同，你只需用鼠标控制酋长。一只手和鼠标就能管理你的强大帝国。不需要对单位进行微观管理，也不需要疯狂的APM（每分钟操作次数）。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109110/extras/82e798266a0fa4c5c91bbf0a5a45e1df.avif?t=1763648269\" width=600 height=96 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109110/extras/35577f3d9101ca8f6eb73ff7d1ba4c62.poster.avif?t=1763648269\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109110/extras/35577f3d9101ca8f6eb73ff7d1ba4c62.webm?t=1763648269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109110/extras/35577f3d9101ca8f6eb73ff7d1ba4c62.mp4?t=1763648269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>要统领这片大地，你的随着季节的节奏。作为一个游牧民族，你的部落需要不时打包迁移，以便寻找更好的资源。更丰富的土地。美好山河，停留不得。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109110/extras/074e7e17d451f5c721f579dc9ad97ac4.avif?t=1763648269\" width=600 height=96 /></span><br>寻找并收获浆果、草药、铜和烟草等资源，并将它们转化为有用的工具、商品、药品和武器。这些物品可供你的部落消耗，也可以用于交易。将马群赶入你的领地，追踪并狩猎野牛，以增加你的食物来源。民以食为天，兵以将为先，有了食物，兵力就可以扩张，美洲大陆就可以随手可得。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109110/extras/19406e385485fd40f3de10c66ec693c7.avif?t=1763648269\" width=600 height=96 /></span><br>寻找其他部落和殖民者，与他们进行交易，与他们为友，或与他们为敌。他们可能会提供你无法制造的物品，武器，也可能只是个草包。殖民者穿着奇怪的服装，痴迷于土地和巩固的建筑物，但是他们拥有先进的技术和武器。他们的知识还可以提升你部落的生存能力和技能。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109110/extras/6f03a292c6a33117a9202e29284b071c.avif?t=1763648269\" width=600 height=96 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109110/extras/9fe314c2da7394f63dea54905b8d2ed0.poster.avif?t=1763648269\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109110/extras/9fe314c2da7394f63dea54905b8d2ed0.webm?t=1763648269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109110/extras/9fe314c2da7394f63dea54905b8d2ed0.mp4?t=1763648269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>话说美洲大事，分久必合，合久必分。盟友随时会变成敌人，敌人也会化敌为友。战争是游戏里无可避免的环节。装备好你的勇士，升级好他们的技能。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解锁技能</h2>通过与他人交换知识，获得新的技能。解锁战士和经济的力量。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >结局</h2>随着殖民者在军事上的技术优势，他们最终会把整个美洲土地慢慢占为己有，并将你赶走。带领你的部落坚守阵地，将他们击退。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109110/extras/2d3e8a9d02a6f23848cc0f7384d44227.poster.avif?t=1763648269\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109110/extras/2d3e8a9d02a6f23848cc0f7384d44227.webm?t=1763648269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109110/extras/2d3e8a9d02a6f23848cc0f7384d44227.mp4?t=1763648269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
